+After installation, Elasticsearch is NOT started automatically. You need to start it manually using the appropriate command for your system:
+
+* For systems using systemd: `sudo systemctl start elasticsearch.service`
+* For systems using SysV init: `sudo service elasticsearch start` or `sudo /etc/init.d/elasticsearch start`
